item.title: " Bout that Life" AAU Basketball and life talk Episode 64: The Evolution of Kobe Byrd, From AAU Basketball to Music & Media Mastery"
item.description: Welcome to the latest installment of the Bout That Life Podcast, broadcasting from the YBA Phenix Fitness 24-7 Basketball Facility in Rocklin, California. In this episode, Your host, Coach C. Collins, dives into the riveting journey of Kobe Byrd, a former AAU basketball player, now thriving as a director, producer, and musical artist. Kobe shares his inspiring transition from basketball dreams to finding his path in media and music after a career-altering injury... Feed: https://feed.podbean.com/boutthatlife/feed.xml

item.title: 416: ‘A Professional Internet User’, With Vlad Prelovac
item.description: Kagi founder and CEO Vlad Prelovac joins the show to talk about the business of web search, the thinking behind Kagi’s own amazing search engine, and their upstart WebKit-based browser Orion. Feed: https://daringfireball.net/thetalkshow/rss
